# CODEOWNERS — change-management control (CICD-3 / ISO 27002:2022 8.32, 8.31, 5.4).
#
# Auto-requests review from the listed owner on PRs touching security-critical
# surfaces. This is the FIRST half of the control; it only ENFORCES review once
# GitHub branch protection on `main` is enabled with "Require review from Code
# Owners" + "Require status checks (CI, Security, CodeQL)". See
# docs/compliance/CHANGE_MANAGEMENT.md.
#
# NOTE: replace @jpss2004-bot with the real GitHub handle/team for the security
# approver(s). An unresolved handle produces only a non-blocking editor warning.

